<div class="ph"><div class="ph-in"><div class="hbadge">À propos</div><h1 style="font-size:clamp(24px,3vw,42px);font-weight:700;color:white;margin-top:12px">Qui sommes-nous ?</h1></div></div>
<div class="fs" style="background:var(--wh);min-height:calc(100vh - 200px)"><div class="fs-inner"><div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:48px">
  <div class="rv-l"><div class="eyebrow">Notre identité</div><h2 style="font-size:24px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:16px"><%- settings.quiSommesNous.title.replace(/innovation/i, "<em>innovation</em>") %></h2><p style="font-size:15px;color:var(--gy);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:14px"><%= settings.quiSommesNous.description %></p><p style="font-size:15px;color:var(--gy);line-height:1.8">Notre ambition est d'inscrire Marrakech et le Maroc dans la dynamique mondiale des villes intelligentes, en valorisant les compétences locales.</p></div>
  <div class="rv-r" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px">
    <div style="background:var(--br);border-radius:8px;padding:28px;color:white"><h3 style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px;opacity:.8">Notre Vision</h3><p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.75;opacity:.9"><%= settings.quiSommesNous.vision %></p></div>
    <div style="background:var(--br-l);border:1px solid rgba(200,132,42,.25);border-radius:8px;padding:28px"><h3 style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px;color:var(--br)">Notre Mission</h3><p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--dk)"><%= settings.quiSommesNous.mission %></p></div>
    <div style="background:var(--wh);border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:8px;padding:28px"><h3 style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:12px;color:var(--br)">Nos Valeurs</h3><div class="tags"><span class="tag">Innovation</span><span class="tag">Durabilité</span><span class="tag">Inclusion</span><span class="tag">Collaboration</span><span class="tag">Excellence</span></div></div>
  </div>
</div></div></div>
